Have you figured out your life yet?

✨ June is Acne Awareness Month ✨
Let’s bust the shame and talk about why pimples happen because it’s not just “bad hygiene” or “junk food”! 💥
Here are real reasons you might be dealing with acne:
🌙 Hormonal changes (PCOD, puberty, periods)

🍔 Diet imbalances (like dairy or sugar spikes)

🧬 Genetics (yep, it can run in the family!)

😓 Stress & lack of sleep (your skin feels it too)

🧼 Over-cleansing or wrong skincare (more is NOT always better)

📱 Dirty pillowcases, phones, and touching your face

💄 Heavy or pore-clogging makeup

Acne doesn’t define beauty.You deserve love and confidence at every stage of your skin journey. ❤️
